structure.unit: LEVEES, DRAINAGE, AND RECLAMATION OF LANDS
MISCELLANEOUS PROVISIONS AS TO DITCHES, DRAINAGE, AND RECLAMATION

law.text: Any board established under this chapter shall comply with the provisions of KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090.
law.history: Created 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 40, sec. 79, effective March 21, 2013.
